import React from 'react'; import { Box, Container, Typography, Grid, Paper, Table, TableBody, TableCell, TableContainer, TableHead, TableRow, Button } from '@mui/material'; import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'; function Dashboard() { // Data dummy untuk tabel pengunjung const visitors = [ { id: 1, name: "John Doe", room: "Standard Room", checkIn: "2025-05-01", checkOut: "2025-05-03", status: "Check-In" }, { id: 2, name: "Jane Smith", room: "Deluxe Room", checkIn: "2025-05-02", checkOut: "2025-05-04", status: "Check-Out" }, ]; return ( {/* Sidebar */} Admin Dashboard {/* Main content */} {/* Stats cards */} Total Check-In 15 Total Check-Out 12 {/* Visitors table */} Daftar Pengunjung Nama Tipe Kamar Check-In Check-Out Status {visitors.map((visitor) => ( {visitor.name} {visitor.room} {visitor.checkIn} {visitor.checkOut} {visitor.status} ))}
); } export default Dashboard;
